{"word":"Months","slug":"months","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Months</b> - 1. Abib, or Nisan, April<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=4'>Ex 13:4</a><p/>2. Zif, May<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=6&verse=1'>1Ki 6:1</a><p/>3. Sivan, June<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=8&verse=9'>Es 8:9</a><p/>4. Tammuz, July<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=39&verse=2'>Jer 39:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=8&verse=19'>Zec 8:19</a><p/>5. Ab, August<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=33&verse=38'>Num 33:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=7&verse=3'>Zec 7:3</a><p/>6. Elul, September<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=6&verse=15'>Ne 6:15</a><p/>7. Ethanim, or Tisri, October<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=2'>1Ki 8:2</a><p/>8. Bul, November<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=6&verse=38'>1Ki 6:38</a><p/>9. Chisleu, December<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=9'>Ezr 10:9</a><p/>10. Tebeth, January<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=2&verse=16'>Es 2:16</a><p/>11. Sebat, February<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=1&verse=7'>Zec 1:7</a><p/>12. Adar, March<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=3&verse=7'>Es 3:7</a>"}]}